WorkItem.Description:
The NuGet package Id should be "HtmlAgilityPack" rather than "HTML Agility Pack". It is more standard to not use spaces. This will allow us to install it like:
Install-Package HtmlAgilityPack
rather than:
Install-Package "HTML Agility Pack"
Â 
not a huge deal, but i had to look up the name to install it since it was not standard.
